Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學園祭即將到來之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟會有這樣的危機造訪輕音社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不錯嘛  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到馬上就能在學園祭上演出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡就很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新兵上陣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年輕音社的演出我也好想看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪去年可是很活躍呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上摔倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把去年學園祭的演出都拍下來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看我想看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓啊  你不再考慮下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放～開～我～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  先從我推薦的經典場景開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啊  梓  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的哦  會被詛咒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:59.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條紋啊條紋～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只有在上場時的演奏才爆種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得會說話了呢～  你這傢伙～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  確實  唯那時候的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  早上爬起來就一副破鑼嗓子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是澪就替你當了主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對梓來說  這將是在輕音社的第一次演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真不錯呢  小澪的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們的興致真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了  你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講堂使用申請書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  學園祭的那份你還沒交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼粗心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  你看我這麼忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年也發生過這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是社團申請…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那麼梓  你來寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…倒也行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  使用者「輕音社」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  名稱是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用樂隊名怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說起來我們樂隊叫什麼名字來著
